SUMMARY:EXHIBITION:  Designing\, Crafting and Building Community: 30 Yea
 rs of Practicing a Design / Build Learning Model
LOCATION:Gould Gallery
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260401
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260502
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-ALLDAYEVENT:TRUE
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event Type";ID=21;TYPE=number:CBE Template
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event Interval";ID=54799;TYPE=CustomAsset:Ong
 oing event
