 ns/nearing-retirement/workshops-prepare-to-retire-from-uw/\n\nWho should
  attend: Employees currently participating in a PERS\, TRS\, SERS or LEO
 FF Retirement Plan and who expect to retire within the next 12 months. P
 lease contact the Department of Retirement Systems (DRS) at to request y
