DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Ongoing event\nCampus room: Online Meeting\n
 Accessibility Contact: mramques@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Information Session
 s\,Meetings\nTarget Audience: Research Administrators\n\nMRAM is a month
 ly meeting open to UW staff interested in research award administration.
  Meetings are jointly hosted by Office of Sponsored Programs and Sponsor
 ed Programs Finance. We provide research administrators at the Universit
 y of Washington with access to timely and relevant information regarding
  award regulation and management.\n\nMRAM website: \nhttps://finance.uw.
 edu/gca/mram\n\nQ&A Instructions for the MRAM webinar: \nUse "Q&A" to as
 k questions\n"Chat" is disabled for attendees in favor of "Q&A"\n\nJoin 
 the MRAM mailing list: \nhttps://mailman23.u.washington.edu/mailman/list
 info/mram/\nSubscribers receive: \n	 - Meeting agenda a few days prior t
 o meetings. 	\n - Meeting reminder with link to attend just before the m
 eeting. 	\n - Meeting materials and Q&A within a week following the meet
 ing. 	\n - Occasional emails with timely and relevant information regard
 ing award regulation and management.
