 thon and Jupyter environments	\n - ...and more\nSelf help and more infor
 mation: Be sure to checkout our documentation: https://hyak.uw.edu with 
 includes step-by-step guides and tutorials\, and our training video coll
 ection: https://hyak.uw.edu/learn.
