SUMMARY:Fundamentals For Startups: the Power of the Pivot
LOCATION:Startup Hall - 1100 NE Campus Parkway\, 2nd floor (take elevato
 r\, opens at 11:30 AM)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T130000
