DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nAccessibility Contact: gal
 enic@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Special Events\nEvent sponsors: Painting + Dra
 wing + Printmaking Program\, Division of Art\n\nPlease join us for this 
 unique opportunity to visit the private studios of the Painting + Drawin
 g MFA students and Division of Art faculty at the School's Sand Point fa
 cilities.\n\nWe will also be celebrating the opening of Rebecca Shippee:
  \nhttps://www.rebeccashippee.net/’s show "Bare Assets" in the Sand Poin
 t Gallery. As part of her full-time teaching position in the Painting + 
 Drawing + Printmaking program\, Shippee's solo exhibition will feature o
 ne 45-foot oil painting. This work was made specifically for the archite
 cture of the gallery\; the three structural steel pillars in the space w
 ill serve as supports for the piece. \n\nStudents\, alumni and the gener
 al public are invited for an evening of conversation\, interaction\, and
  art. RSVP is encourged but not required. Everyone is welcome!\n\nThe Sa
 nd Point Studios + Gallery is located on the second floor of Building 5
