 s among seasoned managers and leaders who bring real-world insights into
  the classroom\, enriching the curriculum with their diverse perspective
 s.\n\nSchedule:\n11:15 am - Park & Walk to the Bank of America Executive
  Center\n11:30 am - Connect with the Student Host & attend Lunch \n12:30
  pm - Technology and Innovation- Professor Suresh Kotha \n3:45 pm - End 
 of Event
