 ne:Chelsea Elkins\, sphaccess@uw.edu
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event Types";ID=30073;TYPE=CustomAsset:Academ
 ics\,Special Events
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event image";ID=40;TYPE=Image:https://www.tru
 mba.com/i/DgCAGueSJhI46bvMAeNIucnC.jpg
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event sponsors";ID=30383;TYPE=MultiLine:Schoo
 l of Public Health\, Office of Public Health Practice
