 tp://facebook.com/UWMusic\nLink: https://music.washington.edu/events/202
 6-04-13/guest-pianist-recital-spencer-myer\n\nThe School of Music keyboa
 rd program presents a solo piano recital by Spencer Myer\, associate pro
 fessor of music at the Jacobs School of Music at Indiana University\, pe
 rforming works by Haydn\, Ravel\, Liszt\, and Carl Vine. \n\n-----------
