DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nOnline Meeting Link: http:
 //washington.zoom.us/j/9684580021\nAccessibility Contact: Nick Stelzner
 \nEvent Types: Workshops\n\nPurple: \nhttps://it.uw.edu/guides/artificial
 -intelligence/purple/ is UW’s general purpose AI tool\, created to suppo
 rt teaching\, research\, and daily operations across campus. It is held 
 once a month for one hour on Zoom. You can attend either part or both. S
