 /1FAIpQLScnmqcYhiUeSAE1gTZObG4RUN6484lk7urWl07uhSPKkOaF5g/viewform?usp=h
 eader\; dinner will be provided from 5-6 p.m. with vegan\, vegetarian\, 
 and nut-free options. Learn more: \nhttps://wellbeing.uw.edu/livewell/ca
 lendar/saam/ about Take Back the Night and Sexual Assault Awareness Mont
 h.
