DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nCampus room: EMBA class ro
 om\nAccessibility Contact: emba@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Lectures/Seminars\n
 Link: https://uwfoster.my.site.com/FosterEvents/s/events-public?eventId=
 a1wa600000D9dib\n\nExperience Foster's EMBA Program\nRegistration is REQ
 UIRED: \nhttps://uwfoster.my.site.com/FosterEvents/s/events-public?event
 Id=a1wa600000D9dib\n\nConsidering an Executive MBA? Let’s Help You Explo
 re It Thoughtfully\n\nBalancing a demanding career\, family commitments
 \, and personal goals makes the decision to pursue an MBA a significant o
 ne. That’s why we invite you to our Experience EMBA event\, designed to 
 give you a clear\, firsthand look at what the journey entails.\n\n&#x1F3
 93\; Step Into the Classroom\nJoin us for a morning session where you'll
  observe a live Executive MBA class in action. You’ll be paired with a c
 urrent student who will share their lived experience in the Executive MB
 A program and answer your questions.\n\n&#x1F4AC\; Experience Dynamic Di
 scussions \nWitness dynamic discussions among seasoned managers and lead
 ers who bring real-world insights into the classroom\, enriching the cur
 riculum with their diverse perspectives.\n\n&#x1F465\; Connect with  the
  Executive MBA program -  Meet one-on-one with either our Executive Dire
 ctor or Admissions Director to discuss how the Executive MBA Program can
  align with your professional and personal aspirations.\n\nSchedule:\n7:
 45 am - Park and walk to the Bank of America Executive Center \n8:00 am 
 - Connect with a Student Host\n8:15 am - Statistics for Management - Pro
 fessor Shaosong Ou\n11:30 am - Lunch with Director of Admissions/Executi
 ve Director and Current EMBA Students\n12:30 pm - End of Event
CATEGORIES:UW Seattle Campus Events
