 http://sustainability.uw.edu/hues" target="_blank">Huskies for Equitable
  Sustainability (HuES)</a>\nLink: https://sustainability.uw.edu/earth-da
 y-2026/stencil\n\nJoin Seattle Public Utilities\, UW Sustainability and 
 Huskies for Equitable Sustainability (HuES) for a hands-on storm drain s
 tenciling: \nhttps://www.seattle.gov/utilities/volunteer/storm-drain-car
 e/stencil-a-storm-drain event to raise awareness about water pollution. 
 Help protect local waterways by marking drains and learning how everyday
  actions impact Lake Washington.\n\nStenciling teams can come to Red Squ
 are on April 21 to pick up paint and stenciling supplies\, and can then 
