 terested in designing a stencil must stop by the Seattle Public Utilitie
 s tent on Red Square on Friday\, April 3 between 11 a.m. and 2 p.m. to c
 heck-in and get all the information about creating a design. All designs
  must be submitted on April 15 for approval.\n\nRegister here: https://f
 orms.gle/YuJDkYP1pfux46ik6
