 t
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event interval";ID=30051;TYPE=CustomAsset:Sin
 gle day event
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Campus location";ID=30032;TYPE=CustomAsset:Bi
 ll & Melinda Gates Center for Computer Science & Engineering (CSE2)
