 ls@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Information Sessions\,Lectures/Seminars\,Special
  Events\nEvent sponsors: Sponsors: Starbucks Workers United\, Young Demo
 cratic Socialists of America\, Harry Bridges Center for Labor Studies\n
 \nA delegation of 8 Brazilian workers who experienced slave-like conditio
 ns at coffee plantations throughout Brazil that directly supplied Starbu
 cks will come to speak to the UW community about their experience and to
