DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nOnline Meeting Link: https
 ://washington.zoom.us/j/93731253101\nAccessibility Contact: finchkn@uw.e
 du\nEvent Types: Academics\,Information Sessions\nEvent sponsors: <a hre
 f="https://it.uw.edu/guides/research/" target="_blank">UWIT Research Com
 puting</a><br /><a href="https://escience.washington.edu/" target="_blan
 k">eScience Institute</a>\nLink: https://washington.zoom.us/j/9373125310
 1\n\nNeed support with your research or project using cloud resources? A
 ttend Cloud Office Hours to get help navigating University of Washington
  cloud services and storage solutions: \nhttps://uwconnect.uw.edu/it?id=
 kb_article_view&sysparm_article=KB0036116 (Amazon Web Services: \nhttps:
 //uwconnect.uw.edu/it?id=kb_article_view&sysparm_article=KB0036102\, Goo
 gle Cloud Platform: \nhttps://uwconnect.uw.edu/it?id=kb_article_view&sys
 parm_article=KB0036117\, and Microsoft Azure: \nhttps://uwconnect.uw.edu
 /it?sysparm_article=KB0034099&id=kb_article_view&sysparm_rank=2&sysparm_
 tsqueryId=1ddd7753c3a3a2104b2073bdc0013147). Meet with a cloud specialis
 ts on UWIT staff who can answer your questions and help you optimize clo
 ud-based workflows.\n\nRegistration is not required. Attendees can join 
 using the Zoom link and must authenticate using a UW NetID or an approve
 d institutional domain.\n\nClick here to Join Cloud Office Hours: \nhttp
 s://washington.zoom.us/j/93731253101\n\nWe Can Help With:\n	 - Getting s
 tarted with UW-supported cloud services: \nhttps://uwconnect.uw.edu/it?i
 d=kb_article_view&sysparm_article=KB0036116	\n - Selecting the right clo
 ud platform or architecture for your project	\n - Managing costs and opt
 imizing cloud resource usage	\n - Moving data to and from cloud platform
 s	\n - Using S3-compatible storage solutions 	\n - Deploying and managin
 g compute resources\, containers\, and workflows	\n - Security and data 
 management best practices	\n - ...and more\nRequest a One-on-One Consult
 ation: \nhttps://uwconnect.uw.edu/it?id=kb_article_view&sysparm_article=
 KB0035552\n\nIf you need dedicated support for a specific project\, you 
 can request a one-on-one consultation with our team. This option is idea
 l for complex workflows\, project planning\, storage design\, or migrati
 on assistance.\nClick here to submit a Research Computing Consultation I
 ntake Form: \nhttps://uwconnect.uw.edu/sp?id=sc_cat_item&sys_id=47d23c5d
 87bd6a50e385333e3fbb356b
