SUMMARY:Laboratory Medicine Grand Rounds: Rida Hasan\, MD - When DAT Isn
 ’t Enough: The Role of Enhanced DAT and Elution Studies in Hemolysis
LOCATION:Magnuson Health Sciences Center D (HSD)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260429T153000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260429T163000
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-ALLDAYEVENT:FALSE
URL:https://dlmp.uw.edu/seminars/laboratory-medicine-grand-rounds
