DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nCampus room: Room 120 Lect
 ure Hall\nAccessibility Contact: ticket@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Screenings
 \nEvent sponsors: Presented in partnership with Meany Center\, the UW Sim
 pson Center for the Humanities\, and the UW Department of Dance.\nLink: 
 https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScjcDCad8BIpDulDFQgVi4JqrD6Xql2
 kk7iAUn0-0_IHheoAQ/viewform\n\nIt seems like two separate realms. One is
  occupied by acclaimed dancers from Brooklyn’s world-renowned Mark Morri
 s Dance Group\, the other by people with Parkinson’s disease. CAPTURING 
 GRACE is about what happens when those two worlds intersect. Filmed over
  the course of a year\, Dave Iverson's remarkable documentary reveals th
 e hopes\, fears\, and triumphs of this newly forged community as they wo
 rk together to create a unique\, life-changing performance.\n\nRegistrat
 ion Link: \nhttps://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScjcDCad8BIpDulDFQg
 Vi4JqrD6Xql2kk7iAUn0-0_IHheoAQ/viewform
