DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nOnline Meeting Link: https
 ://apply.ischool.uw.edu/register/MSIM-StudentPanel-May\nCampus room: Cli
 ck link above to Register\nAccessibility Contact: iask@uw.edu\nEvent Typ
 es: Academics\,Information Sessions\nTarget Audience: Applicants\, Futur
 e Students\nLink: https://ischool.uw.edu/programs/msim\n\nCommunity is t
 he heartbeat of the Information School experience. As a student\, you’ll
  cultivate a vibrant network that will support your journey long after g
 raduation\, opening doors to exciting professional opportunities. \n\nJo
 in us for an engaging panel session with current MSIM students. They'll 
 share their firsthand classroom experiences to provide you with a clear 
 picture of life in the MSIM program. Plus\, our admissions advisor will 
 be on hand to answer all your questions about the MSIM program\, admissi
 on requirements\, and application deadlines. \n\nDon’t miss this chance 
 to gain invaluable insights into the student experience and discover how
  the MSIM program can be your launchpad for success. \n\nTo register or 
 request a recording of the session\, RSVP.  \n\nQuestions about the sess
 ion? Contact an adviser at iask@uw.edu
