 s\, and a performance of School of Music Director Joël-François Durand’s
  Cinq duos. Watras is joined onstage by UW faculty Pala Garcia (violin)
 \, Rachel Lee Priday (violin)\, John Popham (cello)\, Whiting\, and Pacif
 ic Northwest Ballet concertmaster Michael Jinsoo Lim.\n\nTickets: $20 ge
 neral\; $15 UW affiliate\; $10 students/seniors)
