 es: Academics\,Conferences\,Special Events\,Student Activities\nEvent sp
 onsors: The Undergraduate Research Symposium is brought to you by the Of
 fice of Undergraduate Research with the support of Undergraduate Academi
 c Affairs\, the Office of Research\, the Office of the Provost\, and the
  Mary Gates Endowment for Students.\nLink: https://www.washington.edu/ur
 s/\n\nThe Annual Undergraduate Research Symposium is a chance for underg
 raduates to present what they have learned through their research experi
 ences to a larger audience. The Symposium provides a forum for students
 \, faculty\, and the community to discuss cutting-edge research topics an
 d to examine the connection between research and education. The Symposiu
 m includes poster and presentation sessions by students from all academi
 c disciplines and all three UW campuses\, plus invited guests.
