DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nCampus location: Art Build
 ing (ART)\nCampus room: Jacob Lawrence Gallery\nAccessibility Contact: j
 acoblawrencegallery@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Special Events\n\nOur question 
 to consider: What if liberation starts in the body?\n\nThis program is p
 art of the Liberation Book Club at the Jacob Lawrence Gallery. This year
 -long program series hopes to honor our commitment to social justice and
  to gather our community to think about the work of liberation through s
 hared texts\, art\, film\, music\, conversation\, and workshops. Unlike 
 your traditional book club all the reading and study happens together\, 
 so no need to prepare. Join us monthly as we approach the topic of liber
 ation from a number of perspectives. We look forward to being in communi
 ty with you.
CATEGORIES:UW Seattle Campus Events
