DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nAccessibility Contact: uws
 opchoice@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Information Sessions\nEvent sponsors: The 
 CHOICE Institute Certificate Programs\nTarget Audience: Prospective stud
 ents and applicants\nLink: https://washington.zoom.us/meeting/register/w
 UnYMEYDRqWZmiY7EB546w\n\nJoin us for an online information session about
  the Certificate in Data Science Methods for Real-World Evidence in Heal
 th: \nhttps://sop.washington.edu/choice/graduate-education-training-prog
 rams/certificate-in-data-science-methods-for-real-world-evidence-in-heal
 th/. Offered by The CHOICE Institute: \nhttps://sop.washington.edu/choic
 e/ at the University of Washington School of Pharmacy\, this online cert
 ificate is designed to help professionals in biomedical and healthcare i
 ndustries strengthen skills to confidently evaluate and interpret vast a
 mounts of health data. \n\nCourses will help decision-makers understand 
 what data can (and cannot) tell us\, how to choose and trust analytic me
 thods\, and how to translate results into sound decisions in clinical\, 
 regulatory\, and commercial settings. This certificate is especially rel
 evant if you manage data scientists\, collaborate with analytics teams\,
  or make evidence-based decisions. You’ll better assess credibility and 
 communicate findings effectively. \n\nLearn about the certificate's focu
 s and format\, curriculum\, admissions\, application process\, and more
 \, with plenty of time for Q&A. \n\nRegister: Online Information Session 
 for the Certificate in Data Science Methods for Real-World Evidence (RWE
 ) in Health: \nhttps://washington.zoom.us/meeting/register/wUnYMEYDRqWZm
 iY7EB546w
