DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Ongoing event\nOnline Meeting Link: https://
 washington.zoom.us/j/93902130437\nAccessibility Contact: fournier@uw.edu
 \nEvent Types: Special Events\,Workshops\,Not Specified\nTarget Audience
 : Anyone at the UW interested in checking out mindfulness in a friendly
 \, no-pressure environment\nLink: http://tinyurl.com/54hjvh5z\n\nDescript
 ion: We gather weekday mornings at 9:00am on Zoom for a short mindfulnes
 s practice. We settle in for the first few minutes with light guidance t
 hen practice together in silence and end promptly at 9:20. All levels of
