 \,Graduate\,Performances\,Special Events\,Student Activities\nAccessibil
 ity Contact: rovall@uw.edu\nLink: https://www.uwb.edu/alumni/events/both
 ell-block-party\n\nThe UW Bothell Block Party is more than a summer kick
 off — it’s a community-powered celebration of connection\, music and Hus
 ky Pride in the North Sound region. Featuring some of the hottest rising
  bands\, the finest local craft breweries\, food trucks\, outdoor games 
 and much more\, the UW Bothell Block Party has something for everyone. 
 \n\nDetails\nDate: Saturday\, May 30\, 2026\nTime: 2:30 - 8:30 p.m.\nLoca
 tion: Downtown Bothell\n\nSpecial Discounts\n	 - CLASS OF 2026: With gra
 duation around the corner\, you’re our guests of honor! Enter code UWB20
