DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nCampus location: Plant Ser
 vices Building (PSB)\nAccessibility Contact: surplus@uw.edu\nEvent Types
 : Special Events\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/uwsurplus\nTwitter:
  https://twitter.com/UWSurplus\nLink: www.uwsurplus.com\n\nIf you can't 
 make it for the Tuesday Public Store: \nhttps://facilities.uw.edu/uw-sur
 plus/store\, UW Surplus has you covered! Our online storefront: \nhttps:
 //facilities.uw.edu/uw-surplus/store/online-storefront features selected
  items added at 10:00 a.m. every Wednesday. Simply purchase online and p
 ick up within a week - it couldn't be easier!\n\nWhile the best selectio
 n will remain available on Tuesdays\, we're trying to empower more peopl
 e to shop sustainably for furniture\, office essentials\, and more.\n\nU
 W Surplus takes all unwanted items from all UW departments and medical f
 acilities. Our objective is to reuse\, repurpose\, or recycle as many it
 ems as possible to lessen the University’s climate impact on both purcha
 sing and disposal. Items are resold through a retail store and online au
 ctions. We receive new inventory every day\, so our stock is always chan
 ging. If you'd like to get a preview of new items\, you can sign up for 
 our newsletter: \nhttps://facilities.uw.edu/uw-surplus/newsletter-signup
 .
