 mba.com/i/DgAfOQuQAgfoEirm0ap0nagM.jpg
DTSTAMP:20260309T132528Z
DESCRIPTION:Campus room: Online Zoom Training\nAccessibility Contact: sa
 fecampus@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Information Sessions\,Lectures/Seminars\,W
 orkshops\nLink: https://forms.office.com/r/MaUzdEyUtU\n\nDuring this int
 eractive training\, we ask participants to consider their unique role in
  preventing violence at the University of Washington. This training has 
 been adapted to consider the remote academic environments that many staf
 f\, students\, and faculty are currently experiencing. We will explore m
 ental health and warning signs of different forms of violence including
 \; workplace violence\, relationship violence\, sexual harassment\, and s
 talking. We will briefly practice in-person and remote bystander interve
 ntion techniques and build your understanding of UW resources.\n\nClick 
 the link below to register for this training.
