DESCRIPTION:Accessibility Contact: benefits@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Worksho
 ps\nEvent sponsors: UW Human Resources Benefits Office\nLink: https://hr
 .uw.edu/benefits/retirement-plans/nearing-retirement/workshops-prepare-t
 o-retire-from-uw/\n\nWho should attend: Employees currently participatin
 g in a PERS\, TRS\, SERS or LEOFF Retirement Plan and who expect to reti
 re within the next 12 months. Please contact the Department of Retiremen
 t Systems (DRS) at to request your retirement estimate and application o
 r visit www.drs.wa.gov. This 3-hour workshop is designed for those retir
 ing within the year and covers the following topics:\n\n 	 - Retirement 
 eligibility 	\n - Completing the DRS and UW retirement applications 	\n 
 - Retiree medical plan choices and enrollment 	\n - Applying for Medicar
 e 	\n - Leave balances and VEBA\, if applicable 	\n - Notifying your dep
 artment about your separation 	\n - Working after retirement
