 ting/register/tJMpce6vrz8sEtR5miKvhsQiXANt6lBORFTu\n\nNeed support with 
 your High Performance Computing (HPC) project? Attend HPC office hours a
 nd have your questions about the University of Washington's Supercompute
 r Hyak and GPU system Tillicum answered by an HPC expert. Attendees need
  only register once and can attend any of the occurrences with the Zoom 
 link that will arrive via email. Click here to Register for Zoom Office 
 Hours.: \nhttps://washington.zoom.us/meeting/register/tJMpce6vrz8sEtR5mi
 KvhsQiXANt6lBORFTu\n\nWe can help with: \n	 - HPC access for your resear
 ch	\n - Building software containers for your research	\n - Installing s
 oftware packages on our systems	\n - Optimizing your workflows 	\n - Mas
 tering the job scheduler\, Slurm	\n - Using GPUs	\n - Python and Jupyter
  environments	\n - ...and more\nSelf help and more information: Be sure 
 to checkout our documentation: https://hyak.uw.edu/docs with includes st
 ep-by-step guides and tutorials\, and our training video library: https:
 //hyak.uw.edu/learn.
CATEGORIES:UW Seattle Campus Events
