 et="_blank">eScience Institute</a>\nLink: https://washington.zoom.us/mee
 ting/register/tJMpce6vrz8sEtR5miKvhsQiXANt6lBORFTu\n\nNeed support with 
 your High Performance Computing (HPC) project? Attend HPC office hours a
 nd have your questions about the University of Washington's Supercompute
 r Hyak and GPU system Tillicum answered by an HPC expert. Attendees need
