SUMMARY:Gardening with the Seasons: Summer (online)
LOCATION:Online via Zoom
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260618T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260618T203000
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-ALLDAYEVENT:FALSE
URL:https://apps.ideal-logic.com/uwbg?key=2WSB-TGY2T_K9KH-5PTF_d229820c1
 cca
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event Type";ID=21;TYPE=number:UW Botanic Gard
 ens Event
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event interval";ID=30051;TYPE=CustomAsset:Sin
 gle day event
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Accessibility Contact";ID=62969;TYPE=SingleLi
 ne:urbhort@uw.edu
