 b6e
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event Type";ID=21;TYPE=number:UW Botanic Gard
 ens Event
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event interval";ID=30051;TYPE=CustomAsset:Sin
 gle day event
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Campus location";ID=30032;TYPE=CustomAsset:Ce
 nter for Urban Horticulture Complex (CUH)
