DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nOnline Meeting Link: https
 ://washington.zoom.us/j/94285858851\nAccessibility Contact: ats-events@u
 w.edu\nEvent Types: Not Specified\nEvent sponsors: <a href="https://www.
 washington.edu/accesstech/" target="_blank">Accessible Technology Servic
 es</a>\n\nJoin colleagues for this informal networking series with other
  faculty support partners across the UW system for collaborative problem
 -solving. We’ll talk about challenges we face and how we can support fac
 ulty in accessibility efforts in the coming academic year.\n\nThis will 
 be a virtual event taking place on Zoom and captions will be enabled. Th
 is event is intended to be inclusive and accessible. A two-week timefram
 e is necessary to arrange for some accessibility needs. Please email ats
 -events@uw.edu for any accessibility-related requests.\n\nThe University
  of Washington is committed to providing access\, equal opportunity and 
 reasonable accommodation in its services\, programs\, activities\, educa
 tion and employment for individuals with disabilities. To request disabi
 lity accommodation contact the Disability Services Office at least ten d
 ays in advance at: 206.543.6450/V\, 206.685.7264 (FAX)\, or e-mail at ds
 o@uw.edu
