DESCRIPTION:Event interval: Single day event\nAccessibility Contact: uws
 opchoice@uw.edu\nEvent Types: Information Sessions\nEvent sponsors: The 
 CHOICE Institute Certificate Programs\nTarget Audience: Prospective stud
 ents and applicants\nLink: https://washington.zoom.us/meeting/register/p
 tJXj5dvRSOXm26UJDkHPw\n\nJoin us for an online information session about
  the Certificate in Health Economics\, Health Technology Assessment (HTA
 )\, and Market Access: \nhttps://sop.washington.edu/choice/graduate-educ
 ation-training-programs/certificate-in-health-economics-health-technolog
 y-assessment-and-market-access/. Offered by The CHOICE Institute: \nhttp
 s://sop.washington.edu/choice/ at the University of Washington School of
  Pharmacy\, this online certificate is designed for professionals engage
 d in the development\, commercialization\, appraisal\, or evaluation of 
 healthcare technologies—and who are ready to deepen their expertise.  \n
 \nStudents will explore the economic principles that guide healthcare de
 cision-making\, the analytic methods that underpin robust economic evalu
 ation\, and the diverse approaches used by HTA bodies and payer organiza
 tions around the world. \n\nLearn about the certificate's focus and form
 at\, curriculum\, admissions\, application process\, and more\, with ple
 nty of time for Q&A. \n\nRegister: Online Information Session for the Ce
 rtificate in Health Economics\, Health Technology Assessment (HTA)\, and
  Market Access: \nhttps://washington.zoom.us/meeting/register/ptJXj5dvRS
 OXm26UJDkHPw
