SUMMARY:Topics in Clinical Trials: Issues in Non-Inferiority Trials and 
 Addressing Missing Data - Online Short Course
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260710T083000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260710T120000
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-ALLDAYEVENT:FALSE
URL:https://si.biostat.washington.edu/institutes/siscer/CR2604
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event Type";ID=21;TYPE=number:Generic UW Even
 t
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event interval";ID=30051;TYPE=CustomAsset:Sin
 gle day event
